creator: Anzani Machinery S.r.l.
descriptionHtml:
Anzani Smart Operator enhances the performance of the Logimove system. It makes the job of the workers in each working station easier and more interactive. The APP includes all the following features:

• Login with the fingerprint or with id and password (so the system will automatically know who is in the workstation and which operation to send in that workstation)
• Workstation opening/closing
• Call to the manager
• View of the style and operation to be done for each box
• Delay signaling (the screen starts blinging with red color)
• View of the videos of any operation
• Signaling breakdown of the stitching machines, collecting the time of the breakdown
• Database for the machines breakdowns
• Personal performance report
